## 📁 Project Structure (Monorepo)

```
marketmind/                        # Monorepo root
├── apps/
│   ├── electron/                  # Electron desktop app
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── main/             # Electron main process
│   │   │   ├── renderer/         # React app
│   │   │   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   │   ├── services/
│   │   │   │   ├── hooks/       # Including backend hooks
│   │   │   │   ├── store/
│   │   │   │   └── theme/
│   │   │   └── shared/          # Frontend shared code
│   │   └── package.json
│   │
│   └── backend/                  # Backend server
│       ├── src/
│       │   ├── db/              # Database (schema, migrations)
│       │   ├── routers/         # tRPC routers (health, auth, wallet, trading, kline)
│       │   ├── services/        # Business logic (auth, encryption, websocket, binance)
│       │   └── trpc/            # tRPC setup (context, router)
│       └── package.json
│
├── packages/                     # Shared packages
│   ├── types/                   # Shared TypeScript types
│   └── indicators/              # Technical analysis utilities
│
├── scripts/                     # Build and utility scripts
├── docs/                        # Documentation
│   ├── QUICK_START.md          # Quick start guide
│   ├── IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md  # Implementation roadmap
│   └── .github/
│       └── AI_AGENT_GUIDE.md   # Detailed guide for AI agents
├── pnpm-workspace.yaml         # Monorepo configuration
└── package.json                # Root package

Root Commands (pnpm):
  dev:backend      - Start backend server (port 3001)
  dev:electron     - Start Electron app
  build:backend    - Build backend
  build:electron   - Build Electron app
  test             - Run all tests (MANDATORY before commit)
  test:watch       - Run tests in watch mode (dev only)
  lint             - Lint all packages
  type-check       - Type check all packages
  clean            - Clean build artifacts
```

